@Apartment_API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5146

# Module RBAC (tenant access token required; SuperAdmin bypasses)
# Send on every protected /api/ call except /api/v1/auth/*:
#   X-Module-Code: M02          (required — e.g. M02 units/blocks, M04 owners, M05 committee, M10 collections, M11 expenses)
#   X-Permission-Action: Approve  (optional — when HTTP method alone is ambiguous; /approve paths infer Approve)
# GET /api/v1/auth/my-permissions — returns RolePermissions for menu (no X-Module-Code)

### Request login OTP (email in body)
POST {{Apartment_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Auth/login-otp/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com"
}

### Verify login OTP
POST {{Apartment_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Auth/login-otp/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### Apartments (set @token after login-otp/verify)
GET {{Apartment_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Apartments
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Tenant access token (use AccessToken from response as {{token}} for committee APIs — must include apartment_id claim)
# POST {{Apartment_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Auth/tenant-access-token
# Authorization: Bearer <ApartmentSelectionToken>

# --- Committee (JWT must be tenant/apartment scoped, not bare login token) ---
@token = REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN_FROM_TENANT_FLOW

### My module permissions (menu / which X-Module-Code to send)
GET {{Apartment_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/my-permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### All role permissions for current apartment (no X-Module-Code; optional ?roleId=&moduleCode=)
GET {{Apartment_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/role-permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### All modules from dbo.Modules (no X-Module-Code; optional ?isActive=true&moduleGroup=&parentModuleCode=)
GET {{Apartment_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/modules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### All module groups from dbo.modulegroups (no X-Module-Code; optional ?isActive=true)
GET {{Apartment_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/module-groups
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List MC tenures
GET {{Apartment_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/committee-tenures?includeArchived=true&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Module-Code: M05

### Active tenure (detail + embedded members)
GET {{Apartment_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/committee-tenures/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Module-Code: M05

### Create tenure (~1–3 years between dates required: 350–1125 days)
POST {{Apartment_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/committee-tenures
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Module-Code: M05
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenureStartDate": "2026-04-01",
  "tenureEndDate": "2027-06-01",
  "notes": "HTTP test term"
}

### List committee members (optional filters)
GET {{Apartment_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/committee-members?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Module-Code: M05

### Assign member (replace ids from your DB: tenure, person, role)
POST {{Apartment_API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/committee-members
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Module-Code: M05
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "committeeTenureId": 1,
  "personId": 1,
  "committeeRoleId": 1,
  "effectiveFromDate": "2026-04-01"
}

###
